replies.body:
But Ali IS an angry bull. I mean, how pissed off would any other minotaur be if he was put in an arena to fight after having his tribe and family invaded by Noxians? All I have to say is that, just because he is angry, doesn't seem to mean that he is actually evil, because he in fact has all the right to be angry.

*"Yeah... Mundo will need you to come on Saturday!"* {{champion:36}} 
*"Now, I'm angry!* {{champion:12}}
